{"tid":539386,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"警務處女假結婚","createTime":"2018-01-24T13:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:03:50.000Z","uid":63268,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"364c334575bf226af0c29b6bfda15e6a2256db5d","tid":539386,"uid":63268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T13:34:42.000Z","msg":"警務處文書女助理於2011年與內地漢結婚，翌年1月誕下兒子，惟她於同年3月遞交兒子的出生登記文件時卻自稱未婚。至去年入境處調查一宗假結婚案時揭發事件。女助理原被控在出生登記作虛假陳述罪，控方今撤控，改以簽保守行為處理，被告獲准以1,000元守行為12個月，期間不得再犯不誠實的行為。<br />\n<br />\n於警務處法醫科任職的被告周美廷（28歲）被指於2012年3月1日犯案。辯方今指被告月入1.4萬元，而當日遞交的登記表格資料實由被告家人填寫，被告僅簽署確認，由於當時她剛產子不久，精神狀態較差才出現誤會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/213357_04c0654797f570dc0432145f1a250693.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F213357_04c0654797f570dc0432145f1a250693.png&h=8f7551c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180124/57747820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F57747820&d=bGRkWbrMcJKHV6SffWUqVJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=800ec845\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180124%2F57747820&h=091ea895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180124/57747820</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a47504138e107c30bf710b80810cac158ad0da1","tid":539386,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:10:42.000Z","msg":"警察 處女 假結婚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b953aad41073514f8351abedc24b37b79903f487","tid":539386,"uid":75137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T14:22:03.000Z","msg":"48 歲下話"},{"pid":"ed128a8a6